---
title: Speedy Peanut Beef Stir-Fry with Jasmine Rice and Sesame Seeds
description: Looking for a quick and tasty midweek dinner option? Try cooking up our Speedy Peanut Beef Stir-Fry in just 20-25 minutes for a delicious and speedy meal.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R13_W04_UK_QR17243-4_Main_low-947a6a3d.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/655ce20f5234ba85b73b74ff.pdf
author: Sam Richards
time required: 20 minutes
